, New York; Saitoh, T.S., Shimada, T., Hoshi, H., Modeling and simulation of the Tokyo urban heat island (1995) Atmospheric Environment, 30, pp. 3431-3442; Santamouris, M., (2001) Energy and Climate in the Urban Built Environment, , James and James Science Publishers, London; Siegel, R., Howell, J., (2002) Thermal Radiation Heat Transfer, , 4th Edition, Taylor and Francis, New York; Tanimoto, J., Hagishima, A., Chimklai, P., An approach for coupled simulation of building thermal effects and urban climatology (2004) Energy and Buildings, 39, pp. 781-793; Toudert, F.A., Mayer, H., Numerical study on the effects of aspect ratio and orientation of an urban street canyon on outdoor thermal comfort in hot and dry climate (2006) Building and Environment, 41, pp. 94-108; Vasilache, M., Pruteanu, M., Avram, C., Use of waste materials for thermal insulation in buildings (2010) Environmental Engineering and Management Journal, 9, pp. 1275-1280; Wong, N., Jusuf, S.K., Win, A.A., Thu, H.K., Negara, T.S., Xuchao, W., Environmental study of the impact of greenery in an institutional campus in the tropics (2007) Building and Environment, 42, pp. 2949-2970","Sham, J. F. C.; City University of Hong Kong, Department of Building and Construction, Tat Chee Avenue, Kowloon Tong, Hong Kong; email: fcsham@student.cityu.edu.hk",,,,,,,,15829596,,,,"English","Environ. Eng. Manage. J.",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-80052441334
